Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "ExampleDelimiter",ExpressionUUID->"1ca9937e-ea84-4527-b32c-992873ef82e3"],

Cell["\<\
Knoodle's native PD code describes an explicit diagram, one crossing per row. \
A row {a, b, c, d} lists the four arcs meeting at that crossing in \
counterclockwise order, starting from the incoming under-strand arc a. Arcs \
are numbered 0, 1, 2, \[Ellipsis] consecutively along the knot, following its \
orientation (the 0-based analogue of the KnotTheory` convention). An optional \
fifth entry is the crossing's handedness (+1 right-handed, -1 left-handed), \
and two further optional entries give the component colors of the incoming \
under-arc and over-arc, which is how the components of a link keep their \
identity. A PD code for the knot 5_2:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"c514d72b-11f7-4ec3-b6ce-6541c85d4bd7"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"pd52", " ", "=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"6", ",", " ", "9", ",", " ", "7", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"0", ",", " ", "5", ",", " ", "1", ",", " ", "6", ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"4", ",", " ", "1", ",", " ", "5", ",", " ", "2", ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"2", ",", " ", "7", ",", " ", "3", ",", " ", "8", ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"8", ",", " ", "3", ",", " ", "9", ",", " ", "4", ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], "}"}]}], "}"}]}], ";"}], " "}]], "Input",Express\
ionUUID->"98deda33-6081-421e-af5b-7c81c6654197"],

Cell["\<\
Drawing it with orientation arrows and crossing and arc labels shows the \
correspondence. Row 1 is crossing 1: the strand enters along arc 0, passes \
under, and continues as arc 1 -- and {0, 5, 1, 6} reads counterclockwise \
around that crossing, starting from arc 0:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"b99540e6-3dff-43c8-a40e-41a597cb2996"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

