Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "ExampleDelimiter",ExpressionUUID->"64bc2b56-1879-4c75-a04b-7dfc1edc98d5"],

Cell["\<\
Second, KnoodleDraw handles diagrams which are not prime. On the granny knot \
(the connect sum of two trefoils) as a single 6-crossing PD code, DrawPD \
(left) terminates but crushes the two summands into tiny corner tangles; \
KnoodleDraw (right) gives both summands equal weight:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"eb75a00e-3386-4c30-bf70-2f2a067935b1"],

