Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "ExampleDelimiter",ExpressionUUID->"46d21515-d178-4a2d-bb40-3f0e21376326"],

Cell["\<\
Third, complicated diagrams: removing just the three kinks from the 50-gon \
projection above (and simplifying nothing else) leaves a 15-crossing diagram \
that DrawPD can draw -- but with wildly non-uniform crossing sizes (left); \
KnoodleDraw's grid layout (right) keeps every crossing and gap the same size \
no matter how tangled the diagram gets:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"b671d1ef-7375-4244-898e-bec634eadafc"],

